  "title": "Mekanism Eco Energistics",
  "description": "More additional content for Mekanism. New solar panels",
  "body": "\n<a href=\"https://discord.gg/bXgXTa6Wxs\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/discord/1137202630125428868?color=f3f2f4&amp;label=Discord&amp;logo=Discord&amp;logoColor=4d57de&amp;style=for-the-badge\"></a>  ![Static Badge](https://img.shields.io/badge/Supported-5ebfa2?style=for-the-badge&logoColor=4d57de&label=Status&color=5ebfa2)\n<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/mekanismecoenergistics\"><img src=\"https://cf.way2muchnoise.eu/955844.svg\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a>\n\nEco Energistics is an unofficial addon for Mekanism and Mekanism Generators. \n\n\n<font color=\"red\"> In order to run this mod you need: </font><a href=https://modrinth.com/mod/mekanism/version/9.8.3.390><img src=\"https://github.com/AET9RNAL/ModAssets/releases/download/Assets/MekaIcon.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"34\" height=\"34\">||<a href=https://modrinth.com/mod/mekanism-generators/version/9.8.3.390><img src=\"https://github.com/AET9RNAL/ModAssets/releases/download/Assets/MekaIcon.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"34\" height=\"34\"></a>\n\n\nAll solar panels can now function at night, although energy production will be cut in half. All solar panels can now also work when it's raining during the day, with 50% penalization. Raining at night won't cut production even further if you are in a warm biome e.g - desert, but if you are in a wet biome, you will get max possible energy production penalty.\n\n\n\n\n\nAll added content is featured in the list below. Specified solar panel energy production in the list is average.\n\n<details>\n<summary>📋Mod Contents</summary>\n<details>\n<summary>🪟Solar Panels</summary>\n<ul>\n  <li><img src=\"https://github.com/AET9RNAL/ModAssets/releases/download/Assets/EcoEnergistics_Icon_solaradvanced.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"34\" height=\"34\"> - Advanced Solar Panel. Production[650 RF/t]</li>\n  <li><img src=\"https://github.com/AET9RNAL/ModAssets/releases/download/Assets/EcoEnergistics_Icon_hybrid.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"34\" height=\"34\"> - Hybrid Solar Panel. Production[5200 RF/t]</li>\n  <li><img src=\"https://github.com/AET9RNAL/ModAssets/releases/download/Assets/EcoEnergistics_Icon_solarperfecthybrid.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"34\" height=\"34\"> - Perfect Hybrid Solar Panel. Production[10400 RF/t]</li>\n  <li><img src=\"https://github.com/AET9RNAL/ModAssets/releases/download/Assets/EcoEnergistics_Icon_solarquantum.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"34\" height=\"34\"> - Quantum Solar Panel. Production[15600 RF/t]</li>\n  <li><img src=\"https://github.com/AET9RNAL/ModAssets/releases/download/Assets/EcoEnergistics_Icon_solarspectral.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"34\" height=\"34\"> - Spectral Solar Panel. Production[20900 RF/t]</li>\n  <li><img src=\"https://github.com/AET9RNAL/ModAssets/releases/download/Assets/EcoEnergistics_Icon_solarprotonic.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"34\" height=\"34\"> - Protonic Solar Panel. Production[26100 RF/t]</li>\n  <li><img src=\"https://github.com/AET9RNAL/ModAssets/releases/download/Assets/EcoEnergistics_Icon_solarsingular.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"34\" height=\"34\"> - Singular Solar Panel. Production[31300 RF/t]</li>\n  <li><img src=\"https://github.com/AET9RNAL/ModAssets/releases/download/Assets/EcoEnergistics_Icon_solardiffractive.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"34\" height=\"34\"> - Diffractive Solar Panel. Production[36600 RF/t]</li>\n  <li><img src=\"https://github.com/AET9RNAL/ModAssets/releases/download/Assets/EcoEnergistics_Icon_solarphotonic.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"34\" height=\"34\"> - Photonic Solar Panel. Production[125400 RF/t]</li>\n  <li><img src=\"https://github.com/AET9RNAL/ModAssets/releases/download/Assets/EcoEnergistics_Icon_solarneutron.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"34\" height=\"34\"> - Neutron Solar Panel. Production[188100 RF/t]</li>\n</ul>\n</details>\n\n<details>\n<summary>🪟Solar Stations</summary>\n<ul>\n  <li><img src=\"https://github.com/AET9RNAL/ModAssets/releases/download/Assets/EcoEnergistics_Icon_solarstationadvanced.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"34\" height=\"34\"> - Advanced Solar Station. Production[3200 RF/t]</li>\n  <li><img src=\"https://github.com/AET9RNAL/ModAssets/releases/download/Assets/EcoEnergistics_Icon_solarstationhybrid.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"34\" height=\"34\"> - Hybrid Solar Station. Production[20900 RF/t]</li>\n  <li><img src=\"https://github.com/AET9RNAL/ModAssets/releases/download/Assets/EcoEnergistics_Icon_solarstationperfecthybrid.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"34\" height=\"34\"> - Perfect Hybrid Solar Station. Production[41800 RF/t]</li>\n  <li><img src=\"https://github.com/AET9RNAL/ModAssets/releases/download/Assets/EcoEnergistics_Icon_solarstatioquantum.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"34\" height=\"34\"> - Quantum Solar Station. Production[62700 RF/t]</li>\n  <li><img src=\"https://github.com/AET9RNAL/ModAssets/releases/download/Assets/EcoEnergistics_Icon_solarstationspectral.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"34\" height=\"34\"> - Spectral Solar Station. Production[83600 RF/t]</li>\n  <li><img src=\"https://github.com/AET9RNAL/ModAssets/releases/download/Assets/EcoEnergistics_Icon_solarstationprotonic.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"34\" height=\"34\"> - Protonic Solar Station. Production[105000 RF/t]</li>\n  <li><img src=\"https://github.com/AET9RNAL/ModAssets/releases/download/Assets/EcoEnergistics_Icon_solarstationsingular.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"34\" height=\"34\"> - Singular Solar Station. Production[125500 RF/t]</li>\n  <li><img src=\"https://github.com/AET9RNAL/ModAssets/releases/download/Assets/EcoEnergistics_Icon_solarstationdiffractive.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"34\" height=\"34\"> - Diffractive Solar Station. Production[146400 RF/t]</li>\n  <li><img src=\"https://github.com/AET9RNAL/ModAssets/releases/download/Assets/EcoEnergistics_Icon_solarstationphotonic.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"34\" height=\"34\"> - Photonic Solar Station. Production[500000 RF/t]</li>\n  <li><img src=\"https://github.com/AET9RNAL/ModAssets/releases/download/Assets/EcoEnergistics_Icon_solarstationneutron.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"34\" height=\"34\"> - Neutron Solar Station. Production[752800 RF/t]</li>\n</ul>\n</details>\n<details>\n<summary>🔋Tablets</summary>\n<ul>\n  <li><img src=\"https://github.com/AET9RNAL/ModAssets/releases/download/Assets/EcoEnergistics_Icon_energytabletadvanced.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"34\" height=\"34\"> - Advanced Energy Tablet</li>\n  <li><img src=\"https://github.com/AET9RNAL/ModAssets/releases/download/Assets/EcoEnergistics_Icon_energytablethybrid.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"34\" height=\"34\"> - Hybrid Energy Tablet</li>\n  <li><img src=\"https://github.com/AET9RNAL/ModAssets/releases/download/Assets/EcoEnergistics_Icon_energytabletperfecthybrid.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"34\" height=\"34\"> - Perfect Hybrid Energy Tablet</li>\n  <li><img src=\"https://github.com/AET9RNAL/ModAssets/releases/download/Assets/EcoEnergistics_Icon_energytabletquantum.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"34\" height=\"34\"> - Quantum Energy Tablet</li>\n  <li><img src=\"https://github.com/AET9RNAL/ModAssets/releases/download/Assets/EcoEnergistics_Icon_energytabletspectral.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"34\" height=\"34\"> - Spectral Energy Tablet</li>\n  <li><img src=\"https://github.com/AET9RNAL/ModAssets/releases/download/Assets/EcoEnergistics_Icon_energytabletprotonic.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"34\" height=\"34\"> - Protonic Energy Tablet</li>\n  <li><img src=\"https://github.com/AET9RNAL/ModAssets/releases/download/Assets/EcoEnergistics_Icon_energytabletsingular.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"34\" height=\"34\"> - Singular Energy Tablet</li>\n  <li><img src=\"https://github.com/AET9RNAL/ModAssets/releases/download/Assets/EcoEnergistics_Icon_energytabletdiffractive.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"34\" height=\"34\"> - Diffractive Energy Tablet</li>\n  <li><img src=\"https://github.com/AET9RNAL/ModAssets/releases/download/Assets/EcoEnergistics_Icon_energytabletphotonic.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"34\" height=\"34\"> - Photonic Energy Tablet</li>\n  <li><img src=\"https://github.com/AET9RNAL/ModAssets/releases/download/Assets/EcoEnergistics_Icon_energytabletneutron.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"34\" height=\"34\"> - Neutron Energy Tablet</li>\n\n</ul>\n</details>\n<details>\n<summary>🔌Circuits</summary>\n<ul>\n  <li><img src=\"https://github.com/AET9RNAL/ModAssets/releases/download/Assets/EcoEnergistics_Icon_advancedcontrolcircuit.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\"> - Advanced Control Circuit</li>\n  <li><img src=\"https://github.com/AET9RNAL/ModAssets/releases/download/Assets/EcoEnergistics_Icon_hybridcontrolcircuit.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\"> - Hybrid Control Circuit</li>\n  <li><img src=\"https://github.com/AET9RNAL/ModAssets/releases/download/Assets/EcoEnergistics_Icon_perfecthybridcontrolcircuit.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\"> - Perfect Hybrid Control Circuit</li>\n  <li><img src=\"https://github.com/AET9RNAL/ModAssets/releases/download/Assets/EcoEnergistics_Icon_quantumcontrolcircuit.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\"> - Quantum Control Circuit</li>\n  <li><img src=\"https://github.com/AET9RNAL/ModAssets/releases/download/Assets/EcoEnergistics_Icon_spectralcontrolcircuit.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\"> - Spectral Control Circuit</li>\n  <li><img src=\"https://github.com/AET9RNAL/ModAssets/releases/download/Assets/EcoEnergistics_Icon_protoniccontrolcircuit.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\"> - Protonic Control Circuit</li>\n  <li><img src=\"https://github.com/AET9RNAL/ModAssets/releases/download/Assets/EcoEnergistics_Icon_singularcontrolcircuit.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\"> - Singular Control Circuit</li>\n  <li><img src=\"https://github.com/AET9RNAL/ModAssets/releases/download/Assets/EcoEnergistics_Icon_diffractivecontrolcircuit.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\"> - Diffractive Control Circuit</li>\n  <li><img src=\"https://github.com/AET9RNAL/ModAssets/releases/download/Assets/EcoEnergistics_Icon_photoniccontrolcircuit.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\"> - Photonic Control Circuit</li>\n  <li><img src=\"https://github.com/AET9RNAL/ModAssets/releases/download/Assets/EcoEnergistics_Icon_neutroncontrolcircuit.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\"> - Neutron Control Circuit</li>\n\n</ul>\n</details>\n<details>\n<summary>🧈Alloys</summary>\n<ul>\n  <li><img src=\"https://github.com/AET9RNAL/ModAssets/releases/download/Assets/EcoEnergistics_Icon_advancedalloy.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\"> - Advanced Alloy</li>\n  <li><img src=\"https://github.com/AET9RNAL/ModAssets/releases/download/Assets/EcoEnergistics_Icon_hybridalloy.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\"> - Hybrid Alloy</li>\n  <li><img src=\"https://github.com/AET9RNAL/ModAssets/releases/download/Assets/EcoEnergistics_Icon_perfecthybridalloy.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\"> - Perfect Hybrid Alloy</li>\n  <li><img src=\"https://github.com/AET9RNAL/ModAssets/releases/download/Assets/EcoEnergistics_Icon_quantumalloy.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\"> - Quantum Alloy</li>\n  <li><img src=\"https://github.com/AET9RNAL/ModAssets/releases/download/Assets/EcoEnergistics_Icon_spectralalloy.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\"> - Spectral Alloy</li>\n  <li><img src=\"https://github.com/AET9RNAL/ModAssets/releases/download/Assets/EcoEnergistics_Icon_protonicalloy.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\"> - Protonic Alloy</li>\n  <li><img src=\"https://github.com/AET9RNAL/ModAssets/releases/download/Assets/EcoEnergistics_Icon_singularalloy.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\"> - Singular Alloy</li>\n  <li><img src=\"https://github.com/AET9RNAL/ModAssets/releases/download/Assets/EcoEnergistics_Icon_diffractivealloy.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\"> - Diffractive Alloy</li>\n  <li><img src=\"https://github.com/AET9RNAL/ModAssets/releases/download/Assets/EcoEnergistics_Icon_photonicalloy.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\"> - Photonic Alloy</li>\n  <li><img src=\"https://github.com/AET9RNAL/ModAssets/releases/download/Assets/EcoEnergistics_Icon_neutronalloy.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\"> - Neutron Alloy</li>\n\n</ul>\n</details>\n</ul>\n</details>\n\nThe addon is currently in development, bugs are expected, although nothing critical was noticed during the testing. All solar panels all fully functional and configurable.\n\n\nCredits:\nHuge thanks to the Mekanism team for creating Mekanism and it's official addons\n\nPermissions:\n\n1.You are allowed to redistribute this mod as long as You:\n\nI.Must credit the download source as 'CurseForge' or 'Modrinth' and include a direct link that leads to the page of this mod\n\nII.Get personal permission from me in case You plan to publish Your project on CurseForge or Modrinth. Applicable only to CurseForge or Modrinth.\n\n2.You can use this mod in your modpacks\n\n3.You are allowed to modify the source code of the mod",
